Creighton Hale https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Creighton_Hale 0 Creighton Hale (born Patrick Fitzgerald, 24 May 1882 – 9 August 1965) was an Irish-American theatre, film, and television actor whose career extended more than a half-century, from the early 1900s to the end of the 1950s.
